 About IX Power Clean Water  

 IX Power Clean Water is an IX Power LLC company. IX Power is a technology commercialization and product development firm spun-out from Los Alamos National Laboratory in New Mexico.
 
IX Power Clean Water has the opportunity to focus exclusively on the creation of water-related products and services, and can enter into business arrangements with other organizations and
companies.
 
Offices for IX Power Clean Water are located in Albuquerque New Mexico; Golden, Colorado; Milwaukee, Wisconsin; and London, England. 
 
For more information about IX Power LLC, IX Power Energy Machines, and the IX Power Foundation, please visit: www.IxPower.com.
 
Read about some of our Team under the "Leadership" heading above.
   
























