Commercial Services and Supplies

Company Overview of IX Power Clean Water, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
IX Power Clean Water, Inc. designs, manufactures, and sells systems that eliminate organic hydrocarbons in produced water from oil and gas, mining, construction, and industrial processes. The company offers OrganiClear, a treatment system which cleans organic hydrocarbons from produced water for beneficial reuse, such as irrigation, livestock, industrial, and communities. It also provides a Mobile Water Laboratory that supports chemical analysis of surface water, groundwater/precipitation, drinking water, bottled water, agricultural water, urban water supplies, recycled water, general water quality, testing in industrial processes, and industrial and wastewater discharge. The company was inc...
IX Power Clean Water, Inc. designs, manufactures, and sells systems that eliminate organic hydrocarbons in produced water from oil and gas, mining, construction, and industrial processes. The company offers OrganiClear, a treatment system which cleans organic hydrocarbons from produced water for beneficial reuse, such as irrigation, livestock, industrial, and communities. It also provides a Mobile Water Laboratory that supports chemical analysis of surface water, groundwater/precipitation, drinking water, bottled water, agricultural water, urban water supplies, recycled water, general water quality, testing in industrial processes, and industrial and wastewater discharge. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Golden, Colorado with additional offices in Los Alamos, New Mexico; Milwaukee, Wisconsin; and London, United Kingdom. IX Power Clean Water, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of IX Power LLC.
Detailed Description


